StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: GETSTUDENTS
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.GETSTUDENTS(cStudent OUT SYS_REFCURSOR)&lt;br/&gt;IS&lt;br/&gt;begin&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; OPEN cStudent FOR &lt;br/&gt; SELECT Student_table.idPerson, Student_table.surname, Student_table.firstName, &lt;br/&gt; Student_table.title, Student_table.address, Student_table.phone, Student_table.postcode,&lt;br/&gt; Student_table.campusLocation, Student_table.year&lt;br/&gt; FROM Student_table;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;END getStudents;
